title: Goodell, owners expect future vote on LA relocation
text:
> Top News Goodell, owners expect future vote on LA relocation NFL Commissioner Roger Goodell speaks during a news conference at the conclusion of the league's fall meetings Wednesday, Oct. 7, 2015, in New York. Goodell said that he expects NFL owners will vote on franchise relocation to Los Angeles. (AP Photo/Julie Jacobson) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
